snippet.title: Brawl Brothers -SNES- (playthru) (Stage 1)
snippet.description:
Playthru of the SNES beat'em'up 'Brawl Brothers.  This game is fun though fairly typical.  The music is nice and jazzy and the stage designs are fun.  This was one of the first beat'em'ups I ever played and really got me hooked on the genre.  Its fast paced but sometimes the collision detection is a little off.  Still a really worthwhile experience.  :)

Additionally, Kazan is unstoppable.
